    <briefdescription>
<para>Decorator that applies an S-curve (nonlinear) transformation to the control signal. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Converts linear input into an S-shaped curve, useful for smoother starts and finer control in the mid-range. Positive bend values create a softer start, negative values create a sharper initial response.</para>
<para><parameterlist kind="templateparam"><parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>Motor</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>Base motor class (must implement <ref refid="classevam_1_1_curve_decor_1a9c94a0b4947d7135439fce236ddb3b16" kindref="member">Go(signed short)</ref>) </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
<parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>kBend</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>Bend intensity. Range: -10..10. 0 = linear. </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
</parameterlist>
</para>
    </detaileddescription>
